How much time do you spend
to play computer game each day?

2
00:00:05,125 --> 00:00:06,500
Not so much.

3
00:00:06,500 --> 00:00:08,208
I stay up about three days each week.

4
00:00:08,208 --> 00:00:10,583
You will surely die soon.

5
00:00:16,207 --> 00:00:17,625
Aiya.

6
00:00:17,625 --> 00:00:19,583
Wakaba, sorry.

7
00:00:19,583 --> 00:00:21,917
It slipped off my hand.

8
00:00:25,792 --> 00:00:27,333
As if nothing happened.

9
00:00:27,333 --> 00:00:29,333
So annoying.

10
00:00:31,042 --> 00:00:35,083
EPISODE 2: MY HOUSE, ON FIRE?

11
