♫Even my back is full of enemies♫

13
00:00:57,375 --> 00:00:58,750
♫Thousand of creatures♫

14
00:00:58,750 --> 00:01:00,333
♫who are arrogant and ready to charge♫

15
00:01:00,333 --> 00:01:01,417
♫Dive for alive♫

16
00:01:01,417 --> 00:01:02,542
♫Climb for life♫

17
00:01:02,542 --> 00:01:05,083
♫A chaotic state that no one can survive♫

18
00:01:05,083 --> 00:01:09,375
♫Take this as my stage♫

19
00:01:09,375 --> 00:01:10,792
♫Is this over?♫

20
00:01:10,792 --> 00:01:12,875
♫But I'm not done♫

21
00:01:12,875 --> 00:01:15,750
♫Even if you didn't see the fatal silk♫

22
00:01:15,750 --> 00:01:20,875
♫you'll be eaten by me if you fall into the web♫

23
00:01:20,875 --> 00:01:23,458
♫Deeper... inside♫

24
00:01:25,375 --> 00:01:27,625
♫Spider pride made a cruel mark♫

25
00:01:27,625 --> 00:01:30,042
♫in this chest again♫

26
00:01:30,042 --> 00:01:32,208
♫Finding the perfect way isn't enough♫

27
00:01:32,208 --> 00:01:34,625
♫The shredded life must be reformed♫

28
00:01:34,625 --> 00:01:37,042
♫Think desperately♫

29
00:01:37,042 --> 00:01:39,292
♫Fight desperately♫

30
00:01:39,292 --> 00:01:41,583
♫The so-called reality. Feel a bit cold♫

31
00:01:41,583 --> 00:01:44,333
♫Keep living the spider way♫

32
00:01:50,792 --> 00:01:53,458
♫Keep living the spider way♫

33
