364
00:20:05,250 --> 00:20:08,083
What did you say? Evolve?

365
00:20:08,083 --> 00:20:11,208
There are two choices of evolution.

366
00:20:11,208 --> 00:20:13,125
Please choose from below options.

367
00:20:13,125 --> 00:20:14,667
"EVOLUTION OPTIONS"
Hold on a second.

368
00:20:14,667 --> 00:20:16,375
